   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00183"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Wien XVIII</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 7</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00182"/><date>13. 11. 03</date></dateline><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Danke<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr. Ich freue mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr, wenn Du wieder einmal heraus ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t – nur bitte: die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en <date>Sonntag</date> und
                  <date>Montag</date> nicht, weil ich <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01342-1"/>nicht hier<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01342-1">Am <date>Sonntag,
                     15. 11.</date>, besuchte er in <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs> das
                  Grab seiner <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2132 #pmb27667" subtype="implied">Eltern</rs>.</note> bin. Und bitte:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chick mir den <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29855" subtype="implied">Rekurs</rs> gelegentlich zurück.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Dein<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
